OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day with some
OL,6,Fbright and sunny spells. Turning
OL,7,Fcloudier in the late afternoon over
OL,8,FOrkney at first then Shetland later.
OL,9,FLight winds in the morning but
OL,10,Fstrengthening later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA band of rain spreads
OL,13,Feastwards over Orkney this evening,
OL,14,Fdry and cloudy for Shetland.
OL,15,FOvernight, rain spreads into Shetland
OL,16,Fand becomes heavy. Strong
OL,17,Fsoutheasterly winds and risk of gales.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
