OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FCloudy in the morning with
OL,6,Frain clearing to the east. Showers in
OL,7,Fthe afternoon with some bright or
OL,8,Fsunny spells. Strong southeasterly
OL,9,Fwinds becoming westerly, gales
OL,10,Fpossible in the morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FShowers
OL,13,Fand bright spells most of Saturday,
OL,14,Fthen rain and strong winds overnight
OL,15,Finto Sunday. Heavy rain and strong
OL,16,Fwinds clearing to blustery showers
OL,17,FSunday. Dry with sunny spells Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
